Package org.nineml.coffeefilter.exceptions

Class IxmlException

  • java.lang.Object

      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • org.nineml.coffeefilter.exceptions.IxmlException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IxmlTreeException
    public class IxmlException
extends java.lang.RuntimeException
    An Ixml exception.

    IxmlException is just a wrapper around a RuntimeException. It's provided as a convenience for catching errors raised by the Ixml parser.

    See Also:
